### Adim 28 - Duplicate idempotency key ayni response doner
# Ayni idempotencyKey tekrar kullanildiginda yeni payment acilmaz, onceki paymentId doner.
# Expected: HTTP 201 Created + paymentId onceki initiatePayment.response.body.paymentId ile ayni
# @name duplicateIdempotencyKey
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/payments/initiate
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{loginPrimaryUser.response.body.$.accessToken}}

{
  "ticketId": "{{ticketId2}}",
  "provider": "Stripe",
  "idempotencyKey": "{{paymentIdempotencyKey}}"
}

### ==================================================
### TEST SONUCLARI OZETI
### ==================================================
# | Senaryo       | Adim                    | Beklenen       | Kritik mi? |
# |---------------|-------------------------|----------------|------------|
# | Rezervasyon   | Reserve                 | 201 Created    | Evet       |
# | Rezervasyon   | Odeme sonrasi Confirmed | 200 Confirmed  | Evet       |
# | Iade          | Refund sonrasi Available| 200 Available  | Evet       |
# | Race condition| Ikinci reserve          | 409 Conflict   | Evet       |
# | Waiting room  | Join                    | position: 1    | Evet       |
# | Guvenlik      | Token'siz               | 401 Unauthorized| Evet      |
# | Rate limit    | 11. istek               | 429 Too Many Requests | Evet |
